{"tid":1629076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法官拒頒令暫緩新法但下令盡快進行司法覆核聆訊","createTime":"2019-10-06T06:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:37:08.000Z","uid":252013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a23540241654e0d32f30ab0bc217c1460a320c","tid":1629076,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"下月再議...<br />\n<br />\n24名民主派立法會議員，不滿特首林鄭月娥繞過立法會，引用緊急法訂立《禁蒙面法》，更在短時間內生效。議員們認為，緊急法本身已有違憲之嫌，特首只以「公眾危險」為由便行使這權力，認為這做法不妥，擔心這只會激起社會更大的不滿，或甚更大型的示威集會，故要求法庭暫緩法例執行，讓立法會能審議法案。高等法院法官林雲浩聽罷陳辭，拒絕頒下臨時禁制令，但下令盡快進行司法覆核的正審，料審訊將在本月下旬進行，並需時2天，法官要求雙方盡快提供可行日子予法庭。<br />\n緊急法令特首權力過大<br />\n代表泛民議員的資深大律師李...<a href=\"https://headline.appt.cf/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=99244\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.appt.cf%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwd%26id%3D99244&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lCfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=80707549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.appt.cf/share.php?a=headlinewwd&amp;id=99244</a>"},{"pid":"edbd3a9c1563eb0e14f07682c45bd2e26d25ec53","tid":1629076,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2etZjqa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2etZjqa.jpg&h=8cdb81ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcmPGDw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcmPGDw.jpg&h=1a05020d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5a4e7c4c83a4172229cdb833cfeba3019f59de2","tid":1629076,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T06:30:28.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">